did.unittitle: Teacher Preparation and Placement Program, Yale College, records

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The records consist of administrative and student files documenting the Yale Teacher Preparation and Placement Program.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 9-E (YRG 9-E), Records documenting Yale College offices, programs, and projects.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Access to the materials is restricted. See Collection Contents for details.

Original born digital files, as well as preservation masters, may not be accessed due to their fragility. Researchers must consult use copies, or if none exist request that they be made. Born digital files cannot be accessed remotely. System requirements include a Manuscripts and Archives computer and file viewing software.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Teacher Preparation and Placement Program, Yale College, Records (RU 179). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
